#
#   This entry is the TS-Node=182 closing pair that **CLOSES** Axis
#   127 (pure-Rust + pure-Go + pure-JS SSH 2.0 protocol
#   implementation taxonomy) at 1/1/1, completing the triple-182
#   round-number landmark (Rust=182 R1079 _lapdev-cli on russh +
#   Go=182 R1080 _wush on gliderlabs/ssh wrapping x/crypto/ssh +
#   TS-Node=182 R1081 _gondolin on mscdex/ssh2) and marking the
#   **120th axis closed** in the corpus.  R1082 on deck: Rust=183
#   OPENS Axis 128.
#
#   No completion for `gondolin` ships with Apple zsh
